HEADWORD: Fluviometer
<hw>Flu`vi*om"e*ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>fluvius</ets> river + <ets>-meter</ets>.]</ety> <def>An instrument
